&lt;p&gt;While we&apos;re not &lt;em&gt;trying&lt;/em&gt; to break interoperability, please note that we&apos;re not expecting to support 2.12.x servers with 2.16 clients - &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.lustre.org/Release_2.16.0#Test_Matrix&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://wiki.lustre.org/Release_2.16.0#Test_Matrix&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

